#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_polygon2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"A Polygon2D is defined by a set of points. Each point is connected to the"
" next, with the final point being connected to the first, resulting in a "
"closed polygon. Polygon2Ds can be filled with color (solid or gradient) "
"or filled with a given texture."
